# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generic for discover()
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#' Discover information about an object
#'
#' Generic function used for BIDS objects in this phase.
#' @param x Object
#' @param ... Additional arguments passed to methods
#' @export
#' @keywords internal
